Functional requirements:
1- The landlord must be able to publish new ads
2- The system must allow students to find available rooms.
3- The system must allow students to refine their search for available rooms based on specific criteria
4- The system must provide a way for users to communicate and share information
5- The system must keep track of the renter-landlord relationship
6- The system must allow renters and landlords to give feedback on their experience with each other

Non-Functional requirements:
1- Only authenticated lanlords and students should be able to access their respective dashboards
2- A search query must return results quickly
3- The system must have an intuitive and user-friendly interface
4- The system must work on multiple operating systems
5- The plataform must be user-friendly
